{
  "stem": "353.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Gestapo, SS was watching the wires so nobody would-- could go out or in without permission.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Sure, some people had the permit to leave the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You come back in-- in after work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this was the life in ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Ghetto was in one room there were living sometimes 10 and 15 people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And how did-- you maybe question me, how did you and where did you buy food?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was-- there were stores where Germans were allowed to bring some food into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They couldn't starve everybody out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So there was some food in-- in stores in ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then you had to go and look in what store you could buy.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You stay in line sometimes for a few hours until you get a piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And beside this, we were buying on black market.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Where the piece of--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From the Poles, right.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "From between the Pols and Jews.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They made the money.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because if-- if bread was 50 cents, they charged $5 for it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in ghetto, my experience was, at first the Gestapo gave the order that everybody had to have a Kennkarte.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "After the Kennkarte, maybe six months later, they came-- went over the Kennkartes and select people-- who is whom, who is doing work.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they put a blue sticker on the Kennkarte.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This means they was allowed to stay in ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And who couldn't stay in ghetto, they made a transport somewhere to concentration camps or other camps-- labor camps.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Everybody thought that this was gonna be a blitzkrieg, that today is the krieg, then tomorrow we're gonna be all right.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And never in our mind was that the war going to last five years, like it was lasting.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
